@startuml SafeTransfer System Context
title SafeTransfer - System Context

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "API Client\n(Postman / UI / Partner)" as Client

rectangle "SafeTransfer\nSpring Boot Application" as App {
  rectangle "REST API" as RestApi
  rectangle "Wallet, Transfer,\nLedger, Outbox, Audit" as Modules
}

database "PostgreSQL" as Postgres
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
rectangle "Metrics Backend\n(Prometheus compatible)" as Metrics

Client --> RestApi : HTTP JSON\nwallets, deposits, transfers
RestApi --> Modules : application use cases
Modules --> Postgres : transactional state\nwallet, ledger, transfer,\noutbox, audit
Modules --> Kafka : transfer.completed events\nwhen Kafka publishing enabled
Kafka --> Modules : audit listener consumes events
Metrics <-- App : actuator metrics\n/prometheus

note right of App
  Modular monolith.
  Domain modules are separated in code,
  but deployed as one process.
end note

note bottom of Postgres
  PostgreSQL is the source of truth.
  Ledger entries are immutable.
end note

@enduml
